# Brutally Simple Design System Rules

This document defines the design system for integrating Figma designs via the Model Context Protocol (MCP).

---

## 1. Token Definitions

### Colors

Design tokens are defined in `tailwind.config.js` under `theme.extend.colors`:

```javascript
colors: {
  'brand-black': '#030303',    // Primary black - text, buttons, backgrounds
  'brand-white': '#FCFCFC',    // Primary white - backgrounds, text on dark
  'gray-10': '#EDEDED',        // Lightest gray - media placeholder backgrounds
  'gray-20': '#CCCCCC',        // Light gray - separators, disabled states
  'gray-50': '#808080',        // Medium gray - secondary text (socials)
  'gray-60': '#666666',        // Dark gray - labels, metadata text
}
```

**Figma Variable Mapping:**
| Figma Variable | Tailwind Class | Hex Value |
|---------------|----------------|-----------|
| `Black` | `brand-black` | `#030303` |
| `White` | `brand-white` | `#FCFCFC` |
| `Gray/10` | `gray-10` | `#EDEDED` |
| `Gray/20` | `gray-20` | `#CCCCCC` |
| `Gray/50` | `gray-50` | `#808080` |
| `Gray/60` | `gray-60` | `#666666` |

