## 6. Styling Approach

### CSS Methodology
- **Primary**: Tailwind CSS utility classes
- **Custom utilities**: Defined in `src/index.css` via `@layer utilities`
- **Global styles**: Base styles in `@layer base`

### Custom CSS Utilities
```css
@layer utilities {
  .font-extrabold-display {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  
  .squircle {
    corner-shape: squircle;
  }
  
  .will-change-transform {
    will-change: transform, opacity;
  }
}
```

### Base Styles
```css
@layer base {
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }
  
  body {
    font-family: 'Young Serif', serif;
    background-color: #FCFCFC;
    color: #030303;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  }
}
```

### Responsive Design
- Desktop-first approach
- Mobile breakpoint: Uses `h1-mobile` for smaller screens
- Container width: `w-[1440px]` for media sections

