## 8. Animation System

### GSAP ScrollTrigger Hooks
Located in `src/hooks/useScrollAnimation.js`:

| Hook | Purpose | Usage |
|------|---------|-------|
| `useTextScrollAnimation` | Pin & fade text sections | Hero, ProjectCard |
| `useMediaScrollAnimation` | Scale media on scroll | MediaSection |
| `useMediaWithFadeOutAnimation` | Scale + fade out | Last MediaSection |
| `useFooterScrollAnimation` | Scale footer box | Footer |

### Animation Configuration
```jsx
// Text sections
useTextScrollAnimation({
  pinDuration: "85%",    // How long section stays pinned
  scrubDuration: 0.5,    // Smoothing factor
});

// Media sections
useMediaScrollAnimation({
  startScale: 0.85,      // Initial scale
  endScale: 1,           // Final scale
  triggerStart: "top 95%",
  triggerEnd: "top 40%",
});
```

